comment:
Let sit for ~5 minutes.

APPEARANCE: Light Amber, has "legs";

NOSE: Fruity with hints of vanilla; a hit of alcohol, butterscotch;

PALATE: At first sip, tastes a bit thin but gives way to a smooth richness of butter toast, Very smooth, Butterscotch;

FINISH: Not too lingering, oily, beautiful for its price.
